General.Name: Henderson Eurotrust
General.Description: Henderson EuroTrust plc is a closed-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Henderson Investment Funds Limited. It is co-managed by Henderson Global Investors Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of Continental Europe, with an emphasis on Western Europe. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of large and mid cap companies. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the FTSE World Europe (ex UK) Index. Henderson EuroTrust plc was formed in 1992 and is domiciled in the United Kingdom.
